          <p>Enrich your SAP models with live interactive maps, allowing dashboard consumers to analyze business data visually and interactively. Create maps that interact with other components in your dashboard, and combine published geographic data from ArcGIS with SAP BusinessObjects business data for richer analysis. Esri Maps for SAP BusinessObjects seamlessly integrates into the everyday workflows familiar to you and dashboard consumers, without the need for custom coding or GIS expertise. Dashboard consumers require no additional skills or tools to start using map-enabled reports to analyze their data visually; they can view, browse, query, and manipulate the maps in the dashboards using tools and actions that you configure.</p>

