		<h2>What's new</h2>
		<p>Esri Maps for SAP BusinessObjects offers significant updates and enhancements for dashboard designers, consumers, and administrators. Here are some highlights.
		</p>

		<h3>2.0 updates</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Support for dynamic map service layers</li>
			<li>New drawing tools for triggering configured interactive behaviors</li>
			<li>New analysis tools: Filter layer, Measure, and Get route</li>
			<li>Trigger interactive behaviors with the Measure tool, Get route tool, and Find nearby tool</li>
			<li>Configure Infographics and other map tools and settings</li>
			<li>Change the map extent using an overview map and other navigation tools</li>
			<li>Specify any coordinate system when adding XY points</li>
			<li>Configure and apply multiple styles for a layer</li>
			<li>Find hot spots</li>
		</ul>
	
	
